docs.text: Keep Young and Keep Curious 🌟 Tag: Quantum Information, Machine Learning, English Learning Insitution: IFFS UESTC Major: CS Email: yuukikonno1314@gmail.com Welcome to my blog. I am a quantum information, quantum physical, and computer science lover. The majors of my undergraduate and postgraduate both are "Computer Science and Technology", but my postgraduate research is actually quantum information technology. I am a beginner in this field, so if there is anything error or anything ambiguous please let me know. As you can learn from my profile and alias, I am a big fan of YuukiKonno from "Sword Art Online", because she helps me know how precious the life is and how beautiful the hope is. Maybe you have the possibility to get deep feelings about life from her heart-broken but meaningful story. Goal of My Blog 🚩 It helps me have a better understanding of knowledge that I have learned and help me record what I have learned. I appreciate it if this blog gives you some useful information and inspiration Contact me 📫 If you have something interesting want to share with me, feel easy to let me know through my email .
